 mm to 1.1 mm in the CM filtered time\nseries, while it had only a marginal impact on raw time series. This provides a\nstrong evidence that CM filtering is essential for revealing local periodic\nsignals when a millimetre level of accuracy is required.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 17:23:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2021 15:19:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-14"}
