 and spintronics in high-temperature magnets with light elements,\nvanishing net magnetization, and strong spin-coherence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 17:30:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Oct 2021 13:05:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
