ent stellar collapse scenarios. Next generation\ngravitational wave detectors like DECIGO and BBO will be sensitive to the\nneutrino memory effect for supernovae at typical galactic distances and beyond;\nwith Ultimate DECIGO exceeding a detectability distance of 10 Mpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 18:11:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
