haracterization within the moons\nof Miranda, Ariel, and Umbriel, and provide guidance for magnetometer selection\nand trajectory design for future missions to Uranus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 05:25:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
